languages.text: "Нельзя резать! Кровь на нас попадет, а с ней и скверна! Лучше того — сожжем!"
"No, no cutting! We get their blood on us, we'll be tainted too! Better burn 'em!"

languages.text: 「いや、切っては駄目だ！奴らの返り血を浴びたら我々も穢れてしまう！燃やせ！」
languages.original_text: "No, no cutting! We get their blood on us, we'll be tainted too! Better burn 'em!"

traits.locale_text: 「いや、切っては駄目だ！奴らの返り血を浴びたら我々も穢れてしまう！燃やせ！」

languages.text: “不！不能割！要是沾上他们的血，我们也会被污染！最好把他们都烧了！”
languages.original_text: "No, no cutting! We get their blood on us, we'll be tainted too! Better burn 'em!"

languages.text: «¡No, de degollar nada! ¡Que como nos caiga sangre encima, nos infectamos nosotros también! ¡Hay que quemarlos!».
languages.original_text: "No, no cutting! We get their blood on us, we'll be tainted too! Better burn 'em!"

traits.locale_text: «¡No, de degollar nada! ¡Que como nos caiga sangre encima, nos infectamos nosotros también! ¡Hay que quemarlos!».

languages.text: « Non, non, rangez vos couteaux ! S'ils nous aspergent de leur sang, ils nous contamineront ! Il vaut mieux les brûler ! »
languages.original_text: "No, no cutting! We get their blood on us, we'll be tainted too! Better burn 'em!"

languages.text: "Nein, nicht schneiden! Wenn wir ihr Blut abkriegen, sind wir auch befleckt! Verbrennen ist besser!"

languages.text: "Hayır, kesmek yok! Kanları üstümüze sıçrarsa bize de bulaşır! Yakalım daha iyi!"
